98 Update, and I installed it on my home computer. When the
installation was over, I learned three valuable lessons I will
never forget. (Includes 1 column color sig of columnist.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TECHTOOLS: A weather emergency alarm can give you a few
precious extra minutes to get to safety when the weather threatens.
