<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-06 18:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0859 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT-BJT07-COX     07-06 0445
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT07-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
