</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-BARAK (Jerusalem) _ Prime Minister Ehud Barak calls on
Arab countries to make a ``peace of the brave'' as he is sworn in
with a cabinet that left women and Arabs angry at him for not
giving them more cabinet posts. Benjamin Netanyahu says goodbye and
resigns his seat in the parliament. By Aliza Marcus. 1000 words.
