By Jerry Ackerman. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   TV-HOMPEAGES (Undated) _ Firm teams up with a California company
to launch a service that will allow consumers to create
``television homepages.'' Homepages give consumers the opportunity
to buy merchandise related to the TV show they're watching. By
Chris Reidy. 600 words.
</P>
