<P>
   OVERNITE _ Overnite Transportation said it continues to serve
its customers with deliveries despite pickets at company service
centers in metro Atlanta, Memphis, Indianapolis, and Kansas City.
The Teamsters accuse the company of intimidating and even firing
some union organizers working at Overnite. It said the strike would
end when the workers felt their grievances over unfair labor
practices were resolved. (Shelton, Atlanta Jounal-Constitution).
12.
</P>
