   (NYT1) WASHINGTON -- July 6, 1999 -- MCCAIN-PROFILE-1, 7-06 --
Sen. John McCain, R-Ariz., in the Russell Rotunda of the U.S.
Capitol last Thursday. McCain is perhaps the leading underdog for
the Republican presidential nomination. (Shana Raab/New York Times
Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
