<HEADLINE>
WHO IS THIS REPUBLICAN GOVERNOR FROM TEXAS?
</HEADLINE>
 (Resending to restore byline) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
By JAY ROOT 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
